title.narrative: Procurement of goods to undertake land certification and administration

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of goods to undertake land certification and administration) is a component of Land Investment For Transformation (LIFT) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £11,091,213. This component benefits Ethiopia, and works in the following sector(s): Social Protection, Agricultural development, Agricultural land resources, Environmental policy and administrative management, Environmental research, Rural development. , with the following implementing partners: AECOM, Crown Agents Limited, DAI Europe. The start date is 11-03-2014 and the end date is 31-07-2021.
